    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>No Political Correctness</h3>
      <p>Express your political views without fear of censorship.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>No Religious Discrimination</h3>
      <p>Respect for all religions and beliefs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Privacy &amp; Anonymity</h3>
      <p>Your privacy is our priority. We don't track or spy on you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

