  <div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Ruby on Rails</h3>
      <p>Powerful and scalable web development framework.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Bootstrap</h3>
      <p>Responsive front-end framework for faster and easier web development.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
